column3: Diversity in landscape yet not in the riders.
The PNW is awesome! Great videos but not a fan of the expensive lifestyle clothes. Too old, too fat, too slow for Rapha. But I love to ride my  bikes!
To me  simply one of the best Rapha videos....
Great videos. Can't afford to spend that kind of money your clothing.
Great stuff. I am fortunate enough to live in Washington. Great place for riding. Thanks for the video.
Id like to ride with them but I ride a single speed and I'm sure they would frown upon that no matter how bad ass I am.
Great video, May you give me  with the snack recipes ? Thanks you
I wanna be privileged white boy too . . . oh wait, I already am
i think they do, within the cycling community.but u are right, they are very well shot and edited :)
I don't think Rapha gets enough credit for how great these videos are
